'''拉特加萊語'''是一種通行於[[拉脫維亞|拉脫維亞]]東部[[拉特加爾|拉特加爾]]地區的語言。關於拉特加萊語是獨立語言還是拉脫維亞語的方言，現在仍然有爭議<ref>{{cite web|url=http://politika.lv/article/recenzija-par-petijumu-valodas-loma-regiona-attistiba|title=Recenzija par pētījumu "Valodas loma reģiona attīstībā"|last=Druviete|first=Ina|date=22 July 2001|publisher=Politika.lv|language=lv|accessdate=20 August 2013|archive-date=2014-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140518190018/http://politika.lv/article/recenzija-par-petijumu-valodas-loma-regiona-attistiba|dead-url=no}}</ref>。拉特加萊語得到拉脫維亞法律的保護<ref>{{cite web|url=http://likumi.lv/doc.php?id=14740|title=Valsts valodas likums|language=lv|accessdate=15 August 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140209140257/http://likumi.lv/doc.php?id=14740|archive-date=2014-02-09|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

